				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Players can find a few NPCs that have been raised by the myconoid to work as their servants. The party comments on this through a VB.\r\n\r\nThis can fire on any character, and since it is not a result of direct player actions, the replies can be fairly opinionated.\r\n\r\nCan take one or two speakers."
